{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&#xA0;</div></div>", "i": 7349283}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">Por resoluci&#xF3;n exenta N&#xBA; 2.220, de 20 de julio de 2007, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a, autor&#xED;zase a CORPESCA S.A. para realizar actividades extractivas en alta mar con la nave &quot;Angamos 4&quot;, cuyas caracter&#xED;sticas n&#xE1;uticas son las siguientes:</div><br><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Se&#xF1;al distintiva&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; CB-3696</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Puerto de Matr&#xED;cula&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Valpara&#xED;so</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Matr&#xED;cula&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  2633</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Eslora de arqueo&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 29,90 m.</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  T.R.G. (Internacional)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 265,00</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Manga&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  8,92 m.</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Puntal&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3,97 m.</div><br></div>", "i": 7349284}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Valpara&#xED;so, 20 de julio de 2007.- Mar&#xED;a Angela Barbieri Bellolio, Subsecretaria de Pesca (S). </div></div>", "i": 7349285}], "proyectos": [], "otrosSistemas": [], "jurisprudencia": [], "doctrina": [], "metadatos": {"tiene_notas": false, "tipos_numeros": [{"tipo": "3", "numero": "2220 EXENTA", "abreviacion": "RES", "descripcion": "Resolucion", "compuesto": "RES-2220 EXENTA"}], "organismos": ["MINISTERIO DE ECONOMÍA", "FOMENTO Y RECONSTRUCCION", "SUBSECRETARÍA DE PESCA"], "titulo_norma": "", "fuente": "Diario Oficial", "resumenes": [], "materias": [], "terminos_libres": [], "categorias_norma": [], "nombres_uso_comun": [], "paises_tratados": [],